sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant W as Webshop
    participant API as delivery-api
    participant BG as BG task (same process)
    participant DB as DB

    U->>W: Checkout
    W->>API: POST /orders/createorderanddelivery (1st robot)
    API->>API: total capacity = Σ(Product.CapacityL × CartItem.Qty)
    API->>API: required count N = min(CEIL(total / Drone.MaxCapacityL), 3)
    API->>DB: Create parent Order (save TotalCapacityL / RequiredRobotCount) + reserve 1st robot sync
    alt N == 1
        API-->>W: Order completed
    else N >= 2
        API->>BG: Fire-and-forget reservation tasks for the remaining robots
        API-->>W: Order completed (returned immediately, BG not awaited)
    end
    W->>U: Show order completion screen
    loop For each remaining robot (BG, sequential)
        BG->>DB: Reserve robot
        alt Reservation succeeded
            BG->>DB: Create child Order (0 items, 0 JPY, ParentOrderNumber)
        else Reservation failed
            BG->>DB: Set parent Order.RobotShortage = true
            Note over BG: Abort remaining attempts (no retry)
        end
    end
